      <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
      <p class="big-text">
        The Coalition Center for Environmental Sustainability (CC4ES) is a web-based
        center that provides a platform to link coalition members.
      </p>
      <p class="big-text">
        CC4ES is a community of businesses, policy makers and academia who all have
        the common goal of environmental sustainability.
      </p>
      <p class="big-text">
        Linking these members together with dynamic mapping and outreach education,
        CC4ES facilitates a collective shift towards a sustainable future. 
      </p>
    </div>
