        Susan actively engages in various learning disciplines.  She serves as an interdisciplinary adjunct professor at Johnson & Wales University and as a Master Gardener, volunteers as the regional manager for School Garden Mentors for Providence public schools.  Her aim is to link academia and local communities to cultivate internal mind shift for environmentally sustainable living.
      </p>
      <p>
