      <h4>CC4ES Members = CC4ES Dots</h4>
      <p>
        Since CC4ES is the Dot Connector, we would like to refer our members as CC4ES dots. CC4ES members are individual community members in three main groups — businesses and non-Government organizations; academia and other learning communities; and policy makers and government agencies. And you don’t need to be a tree-hugger in order to become a CC4ES Dot.
      </p>
      <p>
        CC4ES is not only for RI. Since it is based on systems thinking, its format can be used in any size and scale.  Although it started in RI, its application reaches beyond RI.
      </p>
